sentences: Sona Shahgeldyan  (Armenian: Սոնա Շահգելդյան, born on November 18, 1986), is an Armenian singer and actress.
Her first video clip was released in 2007.
She won the 2010 edition of New Wave.
2008 – "Menq Miasin enq" (We are together, featuring with Arsen Grigoryan)
2012 – "Haskacel em" (I've understood, featuring with Arsen Hayrapetyan)
